2011 Summer CURIS Sirikata Research Project

Research poster:
    poster.pdf

Demo videos:
    http://goo.gl/5G0B3 for a demo that starts from the beginning
    http://goo.gl/4HB5N for a tour of a finished village

How to configure VillageBuilder in Sirikata:
    Under ogre/scripting:
      villageBuilderHTML.js
      villageBuilder.js

    Under std/graphics:
      villageBulider.em

    In std/graphics/default.em, add the following code in appropriate places:
      system.require('std/graphics/villageBuilder.em;);
      ...
      this._loadkingUIs++;
      this._villageBuilder = new std.graphics.VillageBuilder(this._simulator, ui_finish_cb);
      ...
      this._loadingUIs++;
      this._villageBuilder.onReset(ui_finish_cb);
      ...
      this._binding.addAction('toggleVillageBuilder',std.core.bind(this._villageBuilder.toggle, this._villageBuilder));
      ...
      {key: ['button-pressed'],'m','ctrl'], action: 'toggleVillageBuilder'},

    Under js/scripts/test:
      All remaining .em files
